{
    "tool": {
        "name": "analyze_full_text_tool",
        "description": "Specialized tool for extracting and analyzing all text content from document images while maintaining natural reading order. ONLY use for: documents with mixed text content, articles, reports, books, papers, manuscripts, typed documents, printed text, multi-column layouts, and any content requiring comprehensive text extraction. NOT for: diagrams, tables, handwriting, or specialized scripts. If no readable text is found, returns that no text content was detected and suggests checking with user for appropriate tool selection.",
